extends ../baseEmail

block content
  p Hi,
  p This is a notification to inform you that the password for your #{payload.appInfo.name} account has been successfully updated. We wanted to confirm that the changes you made to your account's password have been applied.
  p If you have recently updated your password, you can disregard this email. However, if you did not initiate the password change, please contact our support team immediately at [#{payload.appInfo.email} or #{payload.appInfo.phone}]. We will investigate any unauthorized activity and take the necessary steps to ensure the security of your account.

  p If you ever need assistance or have any questions regarding your #{payload.appInfo.name} account, please do not hesitate to reach out to our support team. We are here to help.

  small Thank you for being a valued member of the #{payload.appInfo.name} community. We appreciate your commitment to maintaining a secure and supportive environment for all our users.
  br
  small
    b - #{payload.appInfo.email}, #{payload.appInfo.name}